id and Purton remains in the saddle as he comes to this track and trip. May end up back in the run again, but hew may be suited by the bigger track and he can return to form. 7. YOUNG CHAMPION got the job done by 0.3L at this track and trip last time out in this grade. Bowman now hops on board as he rises 1.5kg. Can feature again if he can hold his form. 11. GALACTIC VOYAGE is better than he showed last time out and can bounce back to form today.\",\"runners\":[9,1,7,11],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Tom Wood","tipRunnerNumbers":[11,9,5,1]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,11,9,7]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[8,6,7,1]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[2,9,1,5]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[5,1,4,9]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[9,1,11,12]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[11,12,1,9]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,11,5]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":11,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"DailyDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":9,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Treble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":9,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}}]}}}